1001.Name: Harbor Road West
1001.Desc: A cobblestone street leading east and west. You can hear the market to the west.

1002.Name: Harbor Road East
1002.Desc: A cobblestone street leading east and west. You can hear the harbor to the east.

1003.Name: Harbor Square
1003.Desc: A busy cobblestone square, full of sailors and cargo. Cries of seagulls and the scent of salt fill the air.

1004.Name: Market Road North
1004.Desc: A cobblestone street leading north and south. You can hear the market to the south.
